		{"id":"c870d18de02d14f6","type":"text","text":"# LIBUV\n\nThread pool\n\nFile system\n\nNetwork\n\nprocess\n\n","x":800,"y":-418,"width":400,"height":278},
		{"id":"4a982af46193064c","type":"text","text":"### **Networking (net, http, https, dgram)**\n\nThis is why Node.js is so fast at web servers.\n\n- `http.createServer()` / `server.listen()`\n    \n- `socket.on('data', ...)`\n    \n- `https.request()`\n    \n- `db.query()` (Most DB drivers like `pg` or `mysql2` use non-blocking network sockets).","x":470,"y":-1120,"width":730,"height":380},
		{"id":"92756b923769b7a0","type":"text","text":"### **Compression (zlib)**\n\nAnything involving data shrinking/expanding.\n\n- `zlib.gzip()` / `zlib.gunzip()`\n    \n- `zlib.deflate()` / `zlib.inflate()`","x":1280,"y":-40,"width":438,"height":220},
		{"id":"a71da723adc4b9ab","type":"text","text":"### **Cryptography (crypto)**\n\nCPU-intensive mathematical calculations.\n\n- `crypto.pbkdf2()` (Password hashing)\n    \n- `crypto.scrypt()`\n    \n- `crypto.randomBytes()`\n    \n- `crypto.createHash()`","x":1320,"y":-388,"width":480,"height":248},
		{"id":"245223f5d5755b5d","type":"text","text":"### **File System (fs)**\n\nAlmost all asynchronous `fs` methods use the thread pool.\n\n- `fs.readFile()` / `fs.writeFile()`\n    \n- `fs.stat()`\n    \n- `fs.readdir()`","x":1320,"y":-731,"width":480,"height":223},
		{"id":"36eedad85d4b3041","type":"text","text":"# PENDING","x":120,"y":265,"width":320,"height":50},
